text: Al Balad FC is a professional football club based in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia. The club plays at the Saudi Fourth Division. == Club History == Al Balad FC was established in 2024. The club was born from the passion of local youth and inspired by the culture of Jeddah. Al Balad FC aims to become a leading contender in Saudi football. The club is aims to support local talent and encourage community engagement. == Coaching and Leadership == The coaching team is led by Alejandro Sanchez Vera. It prioritizes skill development, discipline, and nurturing local talent. == References == == Other websites == * Al Balad FC website * Al Balad FC Youtube channel * Category:2024 establishments in Asia Category:Saudi Arabian football clubs
